text:
In case you are still looking for a way to do this. I was able to preset style fields like this on a button.

{% dnd_module
        path="../modules/button",
        offset=0,
        width=12,
        styles={
        'spacing': {
          'spacing': {
            'margin': {
              'top': {
              'value': 20,
              'units': 'px'
              }
            }
          }
        }
        }
      %}
      {% end_dnd_module %}
